Deborah Falconer https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Deborah_Falconer 0 Deborah Falconer (born August 13, 1965) is an American musician and former actress. Her first album was Untangle. She released her second album, Brave Like Me, on July 22, 2003, through Ravish Records. She was also a former Elite Model. Her third album, Lift Your Gaze, was released on October 18, 2014.
